01:09:14.993 --> 01:09:16.792
You feel like laughing,
don't you?

01:09:16.792 --> 01:09:18.793
(LAUGHS)

01:09:18.793 --> 01:09:22.331
JOAN: <i>That kind of invention
only comes from someone who has</i>

01:09:22.331 --> 01:09:25.796
<i>such a deeply rooted sense
of human behavior.</i>

01:09:25.796 --> 01:09:27.670
BURNS: Go ahead,
laugh out loud.

01:09:27.670 --> 01:09:29.304
Don't you see?
Nothing would've made

01:09:29.304 --> 01:09:33.036
Chuckles happier.
He lived to make people laugh.

01:09:33.036 --> 01:09:36.548
So, go ahead, my dear.
Laugh for Chuckles.

01:09:38.617 --> 01:09:39.648
(SOBS)

01:09:39.648 --> 01:09:42.150
JOAN: <i>Mary Richards
was Mary Tyler Moore inside out.</i>

01:09:42.150 --> 01:09:43.718
<i>Everything that was inside Mary</i>

01:09:43.718 --> 01:09:45.653
<i>was right there
in front of the camera</i>

01:09:45.653 --> 01:09:48.961
<i>for people to enjoy, and admire,
and root for.</i>

01:09:50.194 --> 01:09:51.659
We have our very last show...

01:09:51.659 --> 01:09:53.128
- Oh, yeah.
- ...coming up on the filming

01:09:53.128 --> 01:09:54.496
- schedule in three weeks.
- GUEST: No!

01:09:54.496 --> 01:09:56.768
- Yes!
- Yes. And this one's gonna be
a guest on it.

01:09:58.069 --> 01:09:59.267
JAMES: <i>It was on our fifth year.</i>

01:09:59.267 --> 01:10:00.502
<i>And they say,
"Let's go out on top.</i>

01:10:00.502 --> 01:10:02.170
<i>Let's go out
on our sixth season."</i>

01:10:02.170 --> 01:10:04.676
<i>And I said, "Seven."
And they said, "Okay."</i>

01:10:05.977 --> 01:10:08.810
Ted, you're staying.

01:10:08.810 --> 01:10:11.981
And the rest of you guys,
I'm gonna have to let go.

01:10:11.981 --> 01:10:15.383
(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

01:10:15.383 --> 01:10:18.420
- You're letting us go?
- (INDISTINCT CHATTER)

01:10:18.420 --> 01:10:20.121
JAMES: <i>"The Last Show"
was murder</i>

01:10:20.121 --> 01:10:21.690
<i>because of all the attention
we had.</i>

01:10:21.690 --> 01:10:23.758
<i>People writing
about nothing else.</i>

01:10:23.758 --> 01:10:26.698
<i>The world stopped.
She wanted to go out on top.</i>

01:10:28.833 --> 01:10:31.336
Thank you for being my family.

01:10:31.770 --> 01:10:33.705
(SOBS)

01:10:36.908 --> 01:10:38.340
TREVA: <i>Each year,
we all would give</i>

01:10:38.340 --> 01:10:39.908
<i>Christmas presents
to each other.</i>

01:10:39.908 --> 01:10:42.444
<i>You would think a lot
about what to get somebody.</i>

01:10:42.444 --> 01:10:45.881
<i>And a lot of my friends
were reading a book called,</i>

01:10:45.881 --> 01:10:47.515
How to Be Your Own Best Friend.

01:10:47.515 --> 01:10:50.919
<i>I thought of Mary
as been a little way isolated</i>

01:10:50.919 --> 01:10:52.387
<i>and so I bought that for her.</i>

01:10:52.387 --> 01:10:54.890
<i>This was the beginning
of my getting to know</i>

01:10:54.890 --> 01:10:56.291
<i>the fragility.</i>

01:10:56.291 --> 01:11:00.495
<i>And she said,
"Oh, you lovely lady.</i>

01:11:00.495 --> 01:11:03.799
<i>Somebody understands
that I'm not Mary Richards,</i>

01:11:03.799 --> 01:11:07.001
<i>that I'm not happy
all the damn time."</i>

01:11:07.001 --> 01:11:12.072
<i>- ♪ Its a long way to Tipperary ♪
- ♪ Long way to Tipperary ♪</i>

01:11:12.072 --> 01:11:16.078
<i>- ♪ To the sweetest girl I know ♪
- ♪ To the sweetest girl I know ♪</i>

01:11:16.078 --> 01:11:17.279
(SMOOCHES)

01:11:17.279 --> 01:11:19.448
MARY: <i>It had been a whole week</i>

01:11:19.448 --> 01:11:23.284
<i>of intermittent bursting
into sobs for everybody.</i>

01:11:23.284 --> 01:11:25.521
<i>- ♪ Farewell Leicester Square ♪
- ♪ Farewell Leicester Square ♪</i>

01:11:25.521 --> 01:11:27.392
<i>♪ It's a long, long... ♪</i>

01:11:30.361 --> 01:11:32.860
MARY: <i>That moment of going back,
opening the door</i>

01:11:32.860 --> 01:11:36.731
<i>and looking around
at the seven years that faced me</i>

01:11:36.731 --> 01:11:41.073
<i>and that was about to go off,
was sublimely tough.</i>

01:11:51.081 --> 01:11:54.182
ANNOUNCER:
Ladies and gentlemen,
for the last time,

01:11:54.182 --> 01:11:55.887
Mary Tyler Moore.

